        "post": " Wilderness Nature Hokkaido brand Ripe 'n' Dry Soy Sauce Ramen.Hunh?\"We want to design our way of life northern land Hokkaido. Seize the wind, and you will find it you are looking for. We would play in a forest and would catch the fish in a brook.There are wilderness on the earth. There are wilderness on the earth. So we have to keep on protecting. Close your eyes and feel the sound. See, you can hear the voice from nature.\"Delicious.  ",
