        "post": " First, Nagi changed their menu.Second, Kamakura sucked.Third, I show up at this place after riding the motorcycle for 30 minutes, and a nice old man told me:木曜日は休みThursday is the day off.  ",
        "title": " 大勝軒 (Taishoken in Eifukucho) "
