        "post": " ????Sorry, no name of this spot, it was at an onsen beach on the shore of Lake Kussharo.  What is this lake known for?A 20 meter long creature named Kusshii.  Where has he been?  The last sighting was in the 70s...Found 'im!He was swimming in my miso ramen.Actually, this was a tasty bowl!  Not sure what old Kusshii was made of though...  ",
        "title": " さんぱち (Sanpachi in Monbetsu) "
    },
    {
        "date": "2009-09-21 00:00:00",
        "pictures": [
            "http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2537/3934075608_b4940ab53d.jpg",
            "http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2660/3933287567_80f8b19d7c.jpg",
