            "http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2668/3934073936_fb91c7c475.jpg"
        ],
        "post": " 天金One of Keizo's favorites, Tenkin was another must hit spot.This is the truest Asahikawa style ramen there is.The soup takes days to make, but it took me only a few minutes to slurp.Tenkin and Hachiya seem to be in a battle for top spot in Asahikawa these days.  I prefer Hachiya for its stronger soup.  Be sure your try them both, and decide for yourself.Shop info here.  ",
