        "post": " At the annual Mitaka Wish Tree, can you spot my wish?  Its pretty simple, and I'd wager that it has a chance of success about as close to 100% as you could get.2010 was an amazing year for ramen.  Thank you to everyone who read this site, met up for noodles in Tokyo, gave me suggestions, and included me in their own ramen adventures.ごちそうさまでした!  ",
