        "post": " Happy New Year!Regular updates forthcoming.  But in the meantime, I picked up this gift ramen from famous ramen town Onomichi.Having crushed my share of bowls in said ramen destination, this one is for you!To win it, just head over to the Ramen Adventure Facebook page and either \"like\" or leave a comment on this post.  I will choose a winner randomly on January 7th.As long as shipping and all that works out, I hope to have regular ramen contests in the coming year.明けましておめでとうございます！  ",
