        "post": " ソラノイロの夏限定Soranoiro can do no wrong.  The head chef, Miyazaki-san, is a rising star in the ramen scene.  You can be sure that a limited summer special is going to be something fantastic.There is a definite color theme going on here.  Going clockwise, that is gari (pickled ginger), yamaimo (a kind of slimy root vegetable),umeboshi (pickled plum [actually a kind of apricot]), chicken chashu, an egg, and pickled cabbage on the top.  A lot of pickled things means sourness abounds in this one.Add in some lemon jelly.Go ahead!Dump it all in.  Sweet and sour, this cold noodle dish is super fun.You can bet I drained the bowl!Soranoiro has been making a lot of genteis lately.  Keep it up!Soranoiro's Info Here  ",
