        "post": " 庄のの限定    Another over-the-top gentei at Shono.    The soup was a niboshi-shio thing with heavy hits of mushroom. Gnocchi in a cream sauce makes things weird.    And a honey roasted lemon to squeeze on top. Kind of overkill, this one.    Original review here.  ",
