        "post": " 風雲児の限定    I got the last one of the day. Solid!    This 15-a-day limited mazemen is topped with a spicy ground pork mix that puts the kara in karaumai. Definitely not a spice level to be scared of, but up there none-the-less.    Is every good shop making random gentei these days?    Tasty, for sure, but make it a point to stick with the tsukemen if you haven't been to this, my #1 ramen shop in Japan.    Original review here.  ",
