        "post": " ブラク    Soranoiro is constantly doing limited bowls.    This one was black. Deep, black soup. Noodles a few shades from the traditional white. Soy-soaked egg. Black seaweed on top.    Always unique, always great.    And, like all the limited bowls here, gone for months before this post goes live!  ",
        "title": " ソラノイロの限定 (Limited Black at Soranoiro) "
