        ],
        "post": " 麺処GROWTH    Another lunch-only shop in Tokyo that runs out of soup daily.    Another winner. The only thing bad about this place is the name. Growth, when spoken in Japanese, is グロス . . . \"Gross\".    The shop, I should mention, is extremely small. If someone wants to leave, everyone else in the shop has to stand up to let them out. I love it!     View Larger Map   東京都豊島区西池袋3-4-2 Tokyo, Toshima-ku, Nishi Ikebukuro 3-4-2 Closest station: Ikebukuro  Open 11:30-15:30 Closed Sundays  ",
