        "post": " Zoom In Super!    This was the first TV spot I did in Japan, back in 2010. Zoom In Super! is now off the air, but my memories will remain forever. やっぱりうまい！  A very weird experience. The production staff set up a tiny camera in front of me, then left the shop so I could eat with no one around. They wanted reactions, but who over-reacts to food when they are alone. Strange indeed!    We went to three of my favorite shops at the time.  Basanova Fuunji Nagi Shibuya   Hey, these are still three of my favorite shops!        I still have that jacket!    I still have a camera that only focuses in my own hands!  ",
